"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"MASKING","body":"Wh-what? You gonna yell at me just 'cause I might've freestyled a little more than usual today at practice?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"area4473-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"As a producer, any ad-libbing that would disrupt the balance of the song is unacceptable.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"angry02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"area4473-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"But your ad-libbing today felt more like a challenge to the rest of the band. Like you were asking them if they could keep up. That, I welcome wholeheartedly.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":35,"voiceId":"area4473-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":35}],"windowDisplayName":"CHU²","body":"Thanks to you, the rest of the band stepped up their performance considerably.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":35,"motionName":"k